{
  "stem": "1502.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The streets were very dangerous and becoming more dangerous all the time because, as all the Jews that volunteered to come to-- to Mechelen, to camp, that received these subpoenas to come, when that ended, the only Jews they could find is to look for them.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had cars in the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cars had a-- you could recognize, the cars could be recognized that they Gestapo cars because passed the number, it had the letters POL, Polizei.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were roaming around the streets to look for Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was also in Brussels, the Jew, an informant, which was called, we called him [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jack ?] the Informer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Yiddish, they called him [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jack ?] the [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[YIDDISH] means an informer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he was a crazy-- he must've been crazy because his entire family was deported.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he-- he had a talent to recognize Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he was with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was driving around with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He would recognize Jews, stop them in the street and arrest them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And take them away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know the number, but thousands of Jews were discovered in hiding places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Little by little, they found every hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't easy to hide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It became tighter and tighter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The fewer there were left, the more dangerous it became because they didn't have that much jobs, that much work to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were still the same amount of Gestapos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because same way they used the Judenrat, the Jews to facilitate their task by giving them all the addresses of all the Jews, the same way they used the countries where they occupied.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They used the police or they used the local SS that they engaged.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They formed the Belgian SS, and they dressed in black uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
